author: Written by: Sam Winstrom, Assignment Editor
title: Mid-City gas station robbed at gunpoint
text:
NEW ORLEANS (WVUE) - Four armed men held up a Mid City gas station Saturday night.
According to a preliminary report from NOPD, four unknown black males entered the Ideal Gas Station around 10:19 p.m. armed with a shotgun and three hand guns. The four men aimed their weapons on the store's employees and demanded money from the cash registers.
The cashiers complied and emptied the two registers. The suspects then fled on foot in an unknown direction.
Anyone with information on this incident is asked to call CRIMESTOPPERS at 504-822-1111.
